524
00:37:10,519 --> 00:37:13,105
Did you hear what he said
to your future father-in-law?

525
00:37:13,189 --> 00:37:14,398
He's a professor!

526
00:37:15,024 --> 00:37:16,108
He's your professor.

527
00:37:17,068 --> 00:37:19,904
-I haven't been accepted.
