535
00:37:34,043 --> 00:37:36,254
That's why
my father treats me like an idiot.

536
00:37:38,673 --> 00:37:40,174
-Ye-seul.
-Yeong-chang.

537
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:42,718
I love you so much.

538
00:37:43,552 --> 00:37:45,721
