to meddle in our relationship?

544
00:37:59,610 --> 00:38:01,320
You go keep your butt out of pain.

545
00:38:02,655 --> 00:38:03,656
Ye-seul.

546
00:38:07,285 --> 00:38:08,286
Where's Prof. Yang?

547
00:38:09,203 --> 00:38:11,247
