568
00:39:10,181 --> 00:39:11,682
Goodness, it was bait.

569
00:39:11,766 --> 00:39:12,683
But why?

570
00:39:15,061 --> 00:39:16,812
Hey. I'll see you at the Copy Room.

571
00:39:17,521 --> 00:39:20,483
